HOW TO CONTRIBUTE
-----------------
1. Fork the repository on GitHub.
2. Make your changes on a branch.
3. Open a pull request against the main repository.
4. Your contribution must follow the project's coding style and guidelines.

Forks created solely for the purpose of submitting a pull request back to
the original repository are explicitly permitted.
